Text: I've found most home "inspectors" are clueless and miss a lot of things.  I used to get inspections for my properties, now I do them myself.  This book should help others do the same, so save your $300 to $500 and don't hire a guy who was "certified" after a week of "training" or by taking an online course.
A big thank you for this one "THANK YOU"   :)
